<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.8.7">
<l>kiṭantiruntu niṉṟaḷantu kēḻalāyk kīḻpuk</l>
<l>kiṭantiṭun taṉṉuḷ karakku mumiḻun</l>
<l>taṭamperuntō ḷārat taḻuvum pāreṉṉu</l>
<l>maṭantaiyaimāl ceykiṉṟa mālār kāṇparē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He will lie, sit, stand [on her], measure [her], enter below as a boar,</l>
<l>he will dig [her] up he will hide [her] in himself, he will spit [her] out:</l>
<l>Who will see Māl who desired the lady</l>
<l>called “earth” whose big shoulders he fully embraced?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
